  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Fix school damaged by storm</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Tender Talents Magnet School in Kampala, Uganda educates children from disadvantaged backgrounds, offering them secondary school education and housing in a country where publicly funded education ends at grade VII. Our project seeks to repair the water supply and dormitory damaged in a recent storm. A majority of the students are required to live at the school because they come from all over the country. Lack of clean water exposes over 300 children to water born diseases.</narrative>
  </description>
